Postscreen - ChangeLog
======================

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.2.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Removed: Support for i-MSCP 1.3.x Serie
    Review: Refactored code (backend)

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: `POSTFIX_VERSION' parameter not available in Serie 1.3.x
    Fixed: Plugin cannot be reinstalled if it has been uninstalled
    Fixed: Plugin cannot been uninstalled

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Removed: Dead blacklist spamtrap.trblspam.com
    Updated: DNS blacklist and whitelist domains

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.1.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: NiX Spam (ix.dnsbl.manitu.net) to DNS blacklist test
    Added: Postfix version check
    Added: Postscreen dnsbl whitelist threshold
    Changed: Align Postscreen main.cf entries for Postfix
    Changed: Switch Postfix service restart to reload
    Fixed: Postfix (>= 3.0) is showing many warnings about backwards-compatible settings (default setting chroot=y)
    Removed: Experimental smartmatch operator
    Removed: Postfix version check on installation (all supported distributions provide Postfix > 2.8)
    Updated for i-MSCP 1.3.x Serie

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Added: LICENSE file
    Fixed: Don't harcode service configuration file paths
    Fixed: Don't replace smtp service already in master.cf file ( Last definition has higher precedence )
    Removed: Support for i-MSCP 1.1.x serie
    Removed: Mailgraph patch ( Non compliant to the i-MSCP development policy )

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.5
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Removed policyd-weight & postgrey
    Fixed: Catch whether Roundcube is installed

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.4
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Roundcube version 1.x renamed main.inc.php to config.inc.php

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.3
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: my variable $rs and $rdata masks earlier declaration

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Fixed: Uninitialized value $policyService

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

    First release
